name: Knight of the Cloudy Skies
description:
The First of the enigmatic Astral
Knights is the oldest and wisest of the
nine heroes. Though few in number,
they are an ancient clan, and their
mode of war blends spirituality with a
unique mastery of technology. KCS
is a deadly fighter, able to harness the
power of the wind to bring  swift and
silent blows to any who dare oppose
her.
